---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
const updated = "June 2026";
---
<Base title="Now" description="What Shubham Goel is focused on right now.">
  <section class="wrap narrow head">
    <p class="eyebrow">Now</p>
    <h1>What I'm focused on</h1>
    <p class="updated">Last updated {updated}. <a href="https://nownownow.com/about" class="body-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener">What's a now page?</a></p>

    <ul class="now-list stack">
      <li>
        <strong>Going deep on multimodal post-training and evals.</strong> Reading, reimplementing,
        and building small things in the space I want to work in next: getting models to do one
        narrow job extremely well, and the eval harnesses that prove it.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Building in public.</strong> Shipping side projects and writing them up here, from
        a real-time soccer commentary pipeline to a from-scratch VLM challenge set.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Talking to teams.</strong> Exploring what's next, especially frontier-lab and
        consumer-tech work on multimodal models and ranking. If that's you, <a href="mailto:shubhamgoel27@gmail.com" class="body-link">say hi</a>.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Off the keyboard.</strong> Watching too much Arsenal, settling into San Francisco,
        and defending my spot on the poker-nights leaderboard.
      </li>
    </ul>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .head { padding-top: var(--space-2xl); }
  .updated { margin-top: var(--space-xs); color: var(--ink-faint); font-size: 0.88rem; font-family: var(--font-mono); }
  .now-list { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin-top: var(--space-l); font-size: var(--step-0); }
  .now-list li {
    padding-left: var(--space-m);
    position: relative;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .now-list li::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute; left: 0; top: 0.65em;
    width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 2px;
    background: var(--accent);
    transform: rotate(45deg);
  }
  .now-list strong { color: var(--ink); font-weight: 600; }
  .now-list a { color: var(--accent-ink); }
</style>
